data.text: @rebel_grandma I got sick in November. It was rough.  But one thing I would change is all the time I spent worrying if I was sick with every ache, cough and runny nose.  One thing I will say.  You will know if you get it.  Just stay clean and away from people.

@NotJamesAndrews I'm not sure what I can do. I have 2 great-grandbabies due in June from my 2 granddaughters in NC.  My 1st ones.  But I'm beginning to stress over this crap. & my anxiety attacks are getting super bad.  But I'd love to be there when 1 comes home then to my daughters for the 2nd 1
@NotJamesAndrews Lol. Ok 👌  ill consider that.  But what's the chance the mask, 6+ft apart, obsessively washing hands, stay home and now a vaccine,  will keep me safe and not sick?
@rebel_grandma No. They are tracking us because of our cell phones.  We gave that right up years ago. Willingly.  They don’t need to inject us with anything. We are willing to do it ourselves. 🤣😂🤣
